@startuml technician_sequence
!theme plain
title X-ray Technician Sequence Diagram - Image Processing & AI Analysis

actor "X-ray Technician" as tech
participant "System" as sys
participant "Database" as db
participant "File System" as fs
participant "AI Model" as ai
participant "Notification" as notif

== Login ==
tech -> sys: Login
sys -> db: Validate Credentials
db -> sys: Return User Data
sys -> tech: Display Dashboard

== View Pending Requests ==
tech -> sys: View Pending Requests
sys -> db: Query X-ray Requests (status='pending')
db -> sys: Return Request List
sys -> tech: Display Request Queue

== View Request Statistics ==
tech -> sys: View Statistics
sys -> db: Query Request Counts
db -> sys: Return Statistics (pending, completed, total)
sys -> tech: Display Statistics Dashboard

== Process X-ray Request ==
tech -> sys: Select Request
sys -> db: Query Request Details
db -> sys: Return Patient & Request Data
sys -> tech: Display Request Information

tech -> sys: Upload X-ray Image
tech -> sys: Select Image File (JPEG/PNG only)
sys -> sys: Validate File Type
sys -> fs: Store Image File
fs -> sys: Return File Path

sys -> ai: Process Image for Cardiomegaly Detection
ai -> ai: Analyze Chest X-ray
ai -> sys: Return Prediction Result

alt Valid X-ray Image
  ai -> sys: Return (prediction: "positive"/"negative", confidence: float)
  sys -> db: Store Prediction Result
  sys -> db: Update Request Status to 'completed'
  db -> sys: Confirm Storage
  sys -> notif: Notify Requesting Doctor
  sys -> tech: Upload & Analysis Successful
else Invalid Image
  ai -> sys: Return "not_xray" error
  sys -> fs: Delete Invalid Image
  sys -> tech: Error - Not a valid chest X-ray
else Processing Error
  ai -> sys: Return "error" with details
  sys -> fs: Delete Failed Image
  sys -> tech: Processing Failed - Try Again
end

== View Completed Requests ==
tech -> sys: View Completed Requests
sys -> db: Query Completed Requests
db -> sys: Return Completed List
sys -> tech: Display Completed Requests with Results

== Receive Notifications ==
notif -> tech: New X-ray Request Available

@enduml